{Speech 26}{}{The higher command moved him here to serve on Granite's post as I get it. Granite was better, but this guy is not bad too. In spite of that he's constantly yelling with his orders at random persons as we're a part of their "army" too. Most of the time he just sits in the lodge on the first floor drinking as damned.}
